The toolbar "Alister" has the features: 

-Esc button
-Brigtness Dimmer (with fun sun icon)
-Dock - to scroll between open windows
-Spotify - currently playing- tap to go to next song
-Volume - pink to add a little color to an otherwise boring black keyboard
-Sleep button - log off screen goes blanbk
-Timer Tomato - 20 minutes to help focus
-Weather - hyperlink to San Francicso weather station when clicked (you can change to your local)
-Date - Month and day- Hyperlinks to google clanadar (week view) when tapped


enjoy!



